  <div class="section section-center">
    <span class="section-tag">Features</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Everything you need to run efficiently</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Built for production managers who need clarity, speed, and control.</p>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feat-card">
        <div class="feat-icon"><i data-lucide="refresh-cw" style="width:22px;height:22px;color:#4F46E5;stroke-width:2;"></i></div>
