        <p class="feat-desc">Demand data syncs automatically and updates production plans without manual recalculation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card">
        <div class="feat-icon"><i data-lucide="clock" style="width:22px;height:22px;color:#4F46E5;stroke-width:2;"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-title">Save time</div>
        <p class="feat-desc">Eliminate 4–6 hours of daily manual planning. Get actionable plans in under 60 seconds.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card">
        <div class="feat-icon"><i data-lucide="bar-chart-2" style="width:22px;height:22px;color:#4F46E5;stroke-width:2;"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-title">Intuitive charts</div>
        <p class="feat-desc">Visual production summaries make it easy to spot shortage, excess, and scheduling conflicts.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card">
        <div class="feat-icon"><i data-lucide="bell-ring" style="width:22px;height:22px;color:#4F46E5;stroke-width:2;"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-title">Smart alerts</div>
        <p class="feat-desc">Prioritized alerts for low inventory, demand spikes, and machine conflicts — zero noise.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card">
        <div class="feat-icon"><i data-lucide="git-branch" style="width:22px;height:22px;color:#4F46E5;stroke-width:2;"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-title">Full traceability</div>
        <p class="feat-desc">Trace every production decision from demand input to machine output in one click.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card">
        <div class="feat-icon"><i data-lucide="calendar-clock" style="width:22px;height:22px;color:#4F46E5;stroke-width:2;"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-title">Machine scheduling</div>
