      </div>
      <div class="feat-card">
        <div class="feat-icon"><i data-lucide="package" style="width:22px;height:22px;color:#4F46E5;stroke-width:2;"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-title">Inventory health</div>
        <p class="feat-desc">Real-time variant-level inventory monitoring with traffic-light status indicators.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card">
        <div class="feat-icon"><i data-lucide="bot" style="width:22px;height:22px;color:#4F46E5;stroke-width:2;"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-title">Scenario planning</div>
        <p class="feat-desc">Model "what-if" demand scenarios to prepare for seasonal peaks without over-committing.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

