<div class="final-cta">
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <h2>Let your production plan itself.</h2>
    <p>Give thousands of factories an edge by automating their weekly planning and reducing costly floor-level surprises.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/auth" class="btn btn-white btn-xl" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;">
        Start Free — No credit card <i data-lucide="arrow-right" style="width:17px;height:17px;color:#4F46E5;"></i>
